edu.neu.ccis.sms.entity.users.User

  • Packages that use User 
    Package Description
    edu.neu.ccis.sms.dao.categories
    DAO interfaces and implementation classes for manipulating entities like Member, Category, UserToMemberMapping (internal entity which represents the user's registration for a member).
    edu.neu.ccis.sms.dao.users
    DAO interfaces and implementation classes for manipulating entities like User, Team, UserToReviewerMapping (internal entity used in evaluator allocation for submissions).
    edu.neu.ccis.sms.entity.categories
    Hibernate Entity classes for Category, CategoryAttribute (as each category can have multiple different attributes), Member, MemberAttribute (as each member can have its own multiple different attributes), enum MemberStausType, UserToMemberMapping (User's registration for a member)
    edu.neu.ccis.sms.entity.submissions
    Hibernate Entity classes for Document (submission document for a member), Evaluation (evaluation for a document), enum EvalType (signifies different types of final evaluation calculation strategies)
    edu.neu.ccis.sms.entity.users
    Hibernate Entity class for User (SMS user entity) and related enums and classes
